OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe day will have a mostly dry
OL,6,Fbut cloudy start with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers restricted to the Lochaber
OL,8,Farea. Scattered showers spread to most
OL,9,Fparts in the afternoon with some heavy
OL,10,Fand thundery with hail.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe evening will be cloudy
OL,13,Fwith scattered showers, some heavy and
OL,14,Fthundery. These showers become
OL,15,Fisolated from late evening as the odd
OL,16,Fclear spell develops.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
