OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FThe odd shower will die in
OL,6,Fthe early morning to leave a dry but
OL,7,Fcloudy period around midday. Outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain, some heavy, spread northeast
OL,9,Flater.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBands
OL,12,Fof rain push northeast with showers,
OL,13,Fsome heavy and thundery, following
OL,14,FWednesday. These showers continue
OL,15,FThursday morning. A further rain band
OL,16,Fpushes northeast Friday, showers
OL,17,Ffollow later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
